title: CONCRETE Flrs__Granite & Stainless Appliances__SHADY Yard__HUGE Pantry
posting_body: Superb 1 story 4 bedroom 2 bathroom home in the Westgate neighborhood
Spacious living room with skylights on the vaulted ceiling & a floor-to-ceiling brick fireplace
Well-designed kitchen boasts a great U-layout, has plenty of storage in its pantry
Abundance of white cabinets__Stainless appliances: electric range, dishwasher and refrigerator
There is a wonderful family/bonus room that comes complete with built-in shelves
The primary bedroom has a ceiling-fan & walk-in closet
Renovated bathroom, huge mirror and a tiled walk-in shower great for relaxing after a long day
The additional bedrooms share a newly renovated bathroom with a shower/tub combo
Backyard surrounded by trees, with a covered terrace ready to be enjoyed with your loved ones
